207
00:12:27,041 --> 00:12:28,041
Love you.

208
00:12:43,291 --> 00:12:44,916
What were you about to say?

209
00:12:48,208 --> 00:12:49,208
It can wait.

210
00:12:58,500 --> 00:12:59,750
[music stops]

211
00:13:04,458 --> 00:13:06,458
[bells chiming]

212
00:13:12,166 --> 00:13:14,166
[ominous music playing]

213
00:13:21,916 --> 00:13:23,916
[bells chiming continues]

214
00:13:37,583 --> 00:13:41,583
[Dao] Babe, turn off the lights
and shut the doors before coming upstairs.

215
00:13:50,875 --> 00:13:52,875
[music swells]

216
00:13:56,375 --> 00:13:58,375
