220
00:14:31,875 --> 00:14:33,291
[glasses clinking]

221
00:14:39,375 --> 00:14:41,583
-[music swells]
-[bells chiming]

222
00:14:44,625 --> 00:14:45,625
[Dao] Babe.

223
00:14:47,250 --> 00:14:48,583
Babe.

224
00:14:48,666 --> 00:14:51,000
